    public static final class MediaTypeFilter.Builder
extends com.google.protobuf.GeneratedMessageV3.Builder<MediaTypeFilter.Builder>
implements MediaTypeFilterOrBuilder
     This filter defines the type of media items to be returned, for example,
 videos or photos. All the specified media types are treated as an OR when
 used together.
